Data Content: EF 2D BD DD C3 86 39 4E B3 C9 A6 91 B0 9B 58 44 FB 99 E5 19 1B 1F 36 50 7F 61 3E 43 24 CB 99 22
# Block Security Status: 01 = locked, 00 = not locked
